de.unisiegen.tpml.core
Interface AbstractProofModel.UndoableTreeEdit

Enclosing class:
AbstractProofModel
protected static interface AbstractProofModel.UndoableTreeEdit

The base interface for all undoable edit actions on the tree model. Derived classes will need to implement this interface whenever any action on the tree is to be performed.

Method Summary
 void redo()
          Performs the action of this tree edit.
 void undo()
          Undoes the effect of a previous call to redo().
 

Method Detail

redo

void redo()
Performs the action of this tree edit. This method is invoked initially, when the edit is added via AbstractProofModel.addUndoableTreeEdit(UndoableTreeEdit), and when a previously undone change is redone.

undo

void undo()
Undoes the effect of a previous call to redo().
